WEBVTT

00:02.679 --> 00:04.329
NAPOLEON: The time has come, gentlemen.

00:04.439 --> 00:05.804
We are at war again.

00:05.919 --> 00:06.920
Pa, let me enlist.

00:06.999 --> 00:08.000
Absolutely not!

00:08.079 --> 00:09.319
If you won't find me a commission,

00:09.399 --> 00:11.401
I'll run away
and find one myself.

00:11.559 --> 00:14.369
I have fallen in love before
and I expect that I will again.

00:14.759 --> 00:16.682
ILYA: A short time ago,
I was able to be of service

00:16.759 --> 00:19.683
to Princess Marya Bolkonskaya.

00:19.959 --> 00:21.324
Well, it does seem like fate, doesn't it?

00:21.399 --> 00:22.446
(LAUGHS) Yes.

00:22.799 --> 00:23.880
It does.

00:23.959 --> 00:26.246
Just to confirm,
I have received a refusal

00:26.319 --> 00:27.480
from Countess Rostova.

00:27.639 --> 00:30.404
(SOBBING) Will you ask him
if he can forgive me?

00:30.639 --> 00:32.641
No one's as kind as you.

00:32.959 --> 00:35.530
No one understands me
as well as you do.

00:35.599 --> 00:36.600
If you knew how...

00:36.679 --> 00:37.840
Oh, this is wrong.

00:41.319 --> 00:43.367
KUTUZOV: We are fighting
on our own soil now.

00:43.439 --> 00:44.486
Look out!

00:44.799 --> 00:45.880
SOLDIER: Get down, sir!

00:46.399 --> 00:47.605
Kuragin.

00:48.479 --> 00:50.561
(SOBBING)

00:53.159 --> 00:55.639
Napoleon's army has suffered
a mortal wound

00:55.719 --> 00:57.483
from which he will not recover.

00:57.599 --> 00:58.760
Do we go on the offensive?

00:58.999 --> 01:01.127
No, we retreat.

01:01.439 --> 01:02.600
Abandon Moscow?

01:03.719 --> 01:06.723
Abandon Russia's sacred
capital without a fight?

